cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with generating 3D shapes from 2D data, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of neural networks for generative modeling and training techniques falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a proxy neural renderer, which involves neural networks and optimization, falling under neural networks (cs.NE).
